{
  "3234720": {
    "name": "Lugh World",
    "steam_appid": 3234720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>LUGH WORLD – 大型多人捕捉生物冒险</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/9cd38f1aaffd0b2c8ebccfb5544ff553.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=375 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lugh World 是一个大型在线冒险游戏，每一步都开启新的可能性。探索 Miranda 城，捕捉并进化 Lughs —— 充满个性的独特生物 —— 并揭开散布在充满活力、动态变化世界中的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅仅是战斗；更是友谊、竞争以及创造属于你自己的旅程的自由。在 Lugh World 中，你可以与来自世界各地的玩家连接，共享故事，并在不断演变的宇宙中构建回忆。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">将 Lugh World 添加到你的愿望单，准备成为这新时代冒险的先锋之一！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/5dcf7ead02100ac3d69201f6b96ce069.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/5dcf7ead02100ac3d69201f6b96ce069.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/5dcf7ead02100ac3d69201f6b96ce069.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/b3586d8e220d1a01a2458ebde418f2f7.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=375 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入 Lugh World，一个充满独特地区、多样文化和隐藏在每个角落秘密的宇宙。从漂浮的岛屿到冰冻的峡谷，每个环境都带来新的发现和挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这世界的中心是 Miranda，这座繁华城市是玩家的集结点——交易、社交和史诗战斗的枢纽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，真正的主角是 Lughs。这些迷人的生物个性鲜明，拥有元素和特殊能力，使每次遭遇都成为新的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/d8ab16891fad4b768cb0195a3803cc4e.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/d8ab16891fad4b768cb0195a3803cc4e.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/d8ab16891fad4b768cb0195a3803cc4e.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/0e1f9b6548be0745e7aab2dcfd69fc99.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1200 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lughs 是独特的神秘生物，诞生于创造之光！因这特殊的起源，它们拥有惊人的力量和特殊能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/4b40cfb16eed963d99b3372f8562e2be.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/4b40cfb16eed963d99b3372f8562e2be.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/4b40cfb16eed963d99b3372f8562e2be.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/14ec7176623fee0953cb0613fdd60688.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你与 Lughs 一起探索世界，你们都将获得经验并变得更强。Lughs 随着经验的积累可以进化成更强大的新形态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/3e75ac0b63d5d894088cf8b8f387e546.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/3e75ac0b63d5d894088cf8b8f387e546.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/3e75ac0b63d5d894088cf8b8f387e546.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些 Lughs 以线性方式进化：<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/6efa45cfd7d5dec8f4d20918d5304ba3.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1440 height=810 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而另一些则有非线性进化路线：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/81191c3c59a61a10f84283bcb758ff9f.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=810 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，你可以使用特殊道具帮助你的 Lugh 进化，发挥其全部潜力！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/efd460e4659b976a6fd4e359c9b4c6f6.avif?t=1769023408\" width=964 height=524 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/0dc78951593e6eb6d29ac3b9bceef584.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单个 Lugh 可拥有多种形态！发现所有变化——不仅是外观，还有技能和属性。你的收藏在这里具有真正的战略价值！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/e878a4994b425542460cf9122ec32e91.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/e878a4994b425542460cf9122ec32e91.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/e878a4994b425542460cf9122ec32e91.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/59ce2b30e37f00ab3cc583739c357ca3.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >达到最终形态的 Lughs 可以作为坐骑使用！且不仅限于陆地旅行——跑、飞或游泳，Lughs 能带你进入曾经无法到达的新领域。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/802c13a07eb1b54af5686dcee4b5d930.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/802c13a07eb1b54af5686dcee4b5d930.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/802c13a07eb1b54af5686dcee4b5d930.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/6d104d3dc19d9b98829df314f22b3a70.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=171 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用不同类型的水晶捕捉新的 Lughs，扩展你的团队。争取机会获得超稀有的 Lugh，成为受到全世界认可的著名收藏家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/ca119c8c19fb38e72304573f3cd902f3.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/ca119c8c19fb38e72304573f3cd902f3.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/ca119c8c19fb38e72304573f3cd902f3.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/20504ad078b1297952247a98c8135f29.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你的朋友一起面对 Lugh World 的生机勃勃的世界。野生生物、巨大 Boss 和远古神秘等待着冒险者。每场战斗都是获取战利品、积累经验和解锁新挑战的机会。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择战斗方式：通过你的 Lugher 以第三人称视角指挥你的 Lugh，或者直接控制以获得更精准的战术操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/193aaf2bd70b505859bcf09b68925dc9.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/193aaf2bd70b505859bcf09b68925dc9.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/193aaf2bd70b505859bcf09b68925dc9.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/3a53c7c4c98940696cfcadbcb795170e.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有什么比竞技的快感更令人兴奋！向全球玩家发起电力十足的对决挑战。在竞技场中，技巧与策略交锋，只有最强者成为传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/78015f146d14313b60b1ebe3583ead1d.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/78015f146d14313b60b1ebe3583ead1d.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/78015f146d14313b60b1ebe3583ead1d.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/bb56215c1d29e273b99d84fe3913f5d3.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=204 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过直观的界面管理你的 Lughs、装备和资源。整理你的收藏，装备你的伙伴，为任何挑战做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/e0383f4a3d5cb0806a620cf38e7f26b3.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/e0383f4a3d5cb0806a620cf38e7f26b3.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/e0383f4a3d5cb0806a620cf38e7f26b3.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/fa30dd73f6b0b32f958461d82b59f6f1.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=192 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Lugh World 中，每次相遇都可能成为机会。实时与其他玩家交易稀有 Lughs 和珍贵物品，扩大你的收藏并创造新的战略可能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >交易不仅是简单的交换，它是世界中一种社交与经济的纽带，拉近训练师之间的距离，强化社区。每一笔交易都讲述一个故事，可能改变你的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/0076eeaf9b0b620fcd51e827f2ea0664.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=375 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/84f7ee2a667f3b4ae1ee2a424ea3a6f5.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入一个完全在线的 MMORPG，所有事情都实时发生。这里，战斗、遭遇和事件与来自世界各地的成千上万玩家同时展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结盟，和朋友或对手一起探索城市和区域，加入动态活动，沉浸于反映社区力量的繁荣市场。每次游戏都会不一样，因为 Lugh World 的世界永远在进化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一个持久、生机勃勃且充满社交性的宇宙——不仅由其开发者塑造，也由每个冒险者共同创造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/eb622e2aff49c69817b177f683e950b9.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/eb622e2aff49c69817b177f683e950b9.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/eb622e2aff49c69817b177f683e950b9.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/5c9553d6a56bfc13b2d61ba6fdfc2f67.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游戏内任务发现 Lugh World 的故事。探索 Miranda 城及其周边，同时帮助 Lugh 研究中心了解这个世界。与城市行会结盟，前往新区域，深入探寻 Lugh World 的秘密！但要小心——许多挑战在等待，且并非一切如表面所见。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/e299b55314d0a361ab99cea8bedbca32.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=195 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将可以自定义你的角色，展现你的独特风格。但个性不仅限于你的头像——还可以自定义你的 Lughs、家园和装备。你的个人风格是你在世界上的标志！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/f7fd2478bad57270dc50c9c1db2a3c90.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/f7fd2478bad57270dc50c9c1db2a3c90.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/f7fd2478bad57270dc50c9c1db2a3c90.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/cf8acd3edc37d810e1c1ee4b3f812dad.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1200 height=251 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lughpad﻿ 是一种类似于平板电脑的科技设备，供 Lughers 记录他们旅途中遇到的 Lughs。该工具为玩家和 Lugh 研究中心提供宝贵信息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >记录关于 Lughs 的一般数据，编录变种，扩展你对这些令人难以置信的生物的了解。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/2d0d6b59546dcc50f18a0c507b66f336.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/2d0d6b59546dcc50f18a0c507b66f336.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/2d0d6b59546dcc50f18a0c507b66f336.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/61491fb5ec629d520ec800843b2d67c8.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每当你在 Lughpad﻿ 中登记一个新 Lugh 时，你就会获得一张捕获卡！收集这些卡片，可以解锁关于 Lughs 的更多背景和信息。捕捉卡可以包含趣闻、变种细节、稀有度数据等等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/180a552665e67d2792342bc3e176601b.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1318 height=728 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/5b073aef0d8d719e2967a3b2369a2fb1.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/5b073aef0d8d719e2967a3b2369a2fb1.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/5b073aef0d8d719e2967a3b2369a2fb1.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/bec7acc729b7c7f15100b1aa3d629532.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=193 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你的paraglider﻿体验在天空中滑翔的自由！探索新区域，在刺激的空中冒险中翱翔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/f4f88029585e34475f6cb4f0e6433c56.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/f4f88029585e34475f6cb4f0e6433c56.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/f4f88029585e34475f6cb4f0e6433c56.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/71bd1b160bf124515b2a8275fbb04b11.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=196 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参与季节性活动，完成挑战，通过 Lugh World 战斗通行证解锁独家皮肤、称号和装饰性物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成主题任务，解锁传奇皮肤，每个赛季获得独家奖励。战斗通行证鼓励持续参与，用稀有物品、称号和独特定制奖励忠诚度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/5cd27229210697e328d61a97e5b384dd.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一些谜题只有在拼图正确放置后才能解开。准备迎接多个拼图式挑战！请记住：最大的谜团只能由聪明的探索团队揭开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/cc9f51334384324ab40ea592a970796a.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真正可怕的挑战等待着你——愤怒的巨大 Lughs 强大到只有一个大型协调的熟练 Lughers 队伍才能击败它们。这些是 boss 掠夺，合作体验带来巨大的难度和独特的奖赏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他玩家联手，挑战庞大的 Lughs，在历史上留下你的印记！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/61f562e1b7f66c5a53aab448b25895ed.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=375 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lugh World 是一个幻想世界，人类与自然和谐共处，与称为 Lughs 的奇妙生物共享存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人类尊重——有些甚至崇敬——Lughs，世界曾一度和平。但和平并非永恒。一天，一个名叫 Manu 的女孩在海滩上被发现昏迷。她能听懂 Lughs，Lughs 似乎也能理解她。Manu 开始了一段寻找父亲的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多年后，在 Miranda 城，古老的传送门重新激活，许多陌生人出现。他们声称来自名为“地球”的地方，正在寻找 Manu。这些新来者在 Miranda 建立了 Lugh 研究中心，研究这个新世界，它的独特生物（Lughs）并寻找 Manu。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >显然，只有来自地球的年轻人能与 Lughs 正确沟通，从而实现合作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如今，Manu 保护普通人免受时不时出现的愤怒 Lughs 伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，年轻的探险者，是 Lugh 研究中心寻找 Manu 与揭开 Lugh World 秘密的重要盟友！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/6eabdfc44fc2ca3ad7aa727c1f8e978e.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lugh World 由大陆和岛屿组成，拥有多样的生态系统和地形。世界的每个区域都有一个中心城市——社交和经济的枢纽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个区域都有其独特的社会文化动态和历史。过去渴望显现，因为到处都是神秘建筑、废墟、雕像和纪念碑，似乎无人建造。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角落都藏着 Lugh World 的一部分秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/9b7e707c249124bbfd796a21671dca23.poster.avif?t=1769023408\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/9b7e707c249124bbfd796a21671dca23.webm?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/9b7e707c249124bbfd796a21671dca23.mp4?t=1769023408\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234720/extras/e94467410141945623b84291aff5ef4c.avif?t=1769023408\" width=900 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lugh World 中有势力、力量和组织，试图控制 Lughs 及其强大力量以实现自己的野心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三大已知威胁：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>污秽：</strong>其起源与创造之光本身一样古老神秘。当 Lugh 或任何生物被毁灭之影吞噬时，会被污秽污染。在极端情况下，受感染者变成怪物般的暴力存在。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>毁灭使者：</strong>被视为具有邪教性质的组织，力图引导毁灭之影来摧毁世界。传闻毁灭使者精英成员能控制污秽感染的 Lughs，就像 Lughers 能控制普通 Lughs 一样。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>蒙面流浪者：</strong>许多传说讲述了一个戴着白色面罩、披着黑色披风的男子。他出现在废墟或不稳定的水晶释放纯净能量的地区，避免直接接触，远远观察，但会留下神秘的符号——刻在石头上的象形文字和似乎包含地球文字的符文。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>注意：文本可能包含翻译错误。如果您发现任何错误，请联系我们以便我们进行修正。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
